parameters: We're finally at the volcano! Man is it hot here. Let's gather
up some soul energy so we can get outta here!
With my amplifier back, I can dish out some wicked attacks!
Press 'E' to launch out a sound-wave attack! Using a sound-wave will
use up all your 'Combo!', dealing more damage the higher it is!
Defeat enemies to gather soul energy. When the soul gauge is full,
press 'Q' to unleash a massive super attack!
